{"id": 2274, "genre": 1001, "title": "出门旅行，你有哪些“自认为是个有品的消费者”但还是不小心掉坑里的经历？", "description": "比坚持做自己更难的是，在旅行途中坚持做自己。（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 1734, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180410162940IPx2BqfuL3Us6cnC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 275201, "content": "必去景点\n特色名小吃\n去过的人都怎么怎么样了╮（╯＿╰）╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307392}, {"id": 275202, "content": "“当地特色”都可以以更低的价格网购到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118633}, {"id": 275203, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064383}, {"id": 275715, "content": "我是个不理智的消费者 看到东西就想买 尤其是衣服 试完了又不得不买 买完了又后悔 这是一种“病”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314799}, {"id": 275204, "content": "讲真，不懂的时候多看不下决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791306}, {"id": 277253, "content": "来都来了总要尝试点当地的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293385}, {"id": 275207, "content": "买个开心—“只有这里可以买得到”，来都来了，多花点钱也没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947048}, {"id": 275209, "content": "        这家店是导游让我们去的，然后我觉得肯定是那种坑消费者的提成的店，然后我去了这家店附近的另一家类似的店，然后，我美滋滋买完东西出门的时候，看到了另一个旅游团的导游，带着游客们进来了。", "image": "img/option/option/20180411171923x9GMcEhrW1bNywq6.jpg", "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311274}, {"id": 275212, "content": "去之前网上做攻略，攻略的景点基本热门景点，然后…死循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301248}, {"id": 274957, "content": "决不在旅游景点买东西，但每次看日出都不得不现场租个军大衣/买个披肩", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275213, "content": "在东京用Google搜索最受欢迎的美食，第一名全聚德，第二名风荷苑。走了1.5公里发现风荷苑是个四川料理。最后吃了麦当当。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 83814}, {"id": 274958, "content": "机场里的特产都太普通没心意……但每次都忘记买伴手礼最后只能机场凑合一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275214, "content": "报道☕️", "image": "img/option/option/20180411180834QVf1lM7aGxO03RiK.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311236}, {"id": 274959, "content": "早就想好了吃点当地苍蝇馆子，结果一直被包车司机带去有回扣的团餐餐厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275218, "content": "所谓当地美食", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 275219, "content": "去小吃街吃东西！超级难吃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311333}, {"id": 275220, "content": "都是网上和自己城市都能买到的东西，但就是为了证明“这东西是我当地买的！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307808}, {"id": 275221, "content": "四川人去杭州吃不惯江浙菜，最后吃了很火的“陈小姐在成都”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311345}, {"id": 275222, "content": "排队两小时买喜茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311345}, {"id": 275225, "content": "打小卡片上的电话?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280012}, {"id": 275226, "content": "过年加费用服务还打折", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 275227, "content": "q", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306658}, {"id": 275228, "content": "清明出去玩买了茶叶，一小罐20不贵，茶叶也还不错。到下一家，同样20重量却多了一倍，算了一下一斤分别480和960左右。事实证明，虽然掉坑了但不影响我有品，茶挺香哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 275229, "content": "哪儿都能买到的东西我才不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 275230, "content": "根本就没有休闲旅游这种东西，旅和游就是体力活，不亚于搬砖。要休闲的话最好就去度假酒店呆着。", "image": "img/option/option/20180411194629gsaZuG0QiS2o9WxJ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067780}, {"id": 275231, "content": "但出去玩 不就是想体验下当地人的生活吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256239}, {"id": 275232, "content": "被坑了还得笑着给服务员小费", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311471}, {"id": 275233, "content": "嗯嗯嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311470}, {"id": 275235, "content": "正宗老北京油炸臭豆腐，正宗老北京花生糖……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42341}, {"id": 275236, "content": "有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311499}, {"id": 275238, "content": "海鲜总归是贵的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311532}, {"id": 275495, "content": "从来不会买旅游景点的东西，除非特别喜欢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313070}, {"id": 275497, "content": "因为时间来不及，不得不买电影院卖的瓶装饮料", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313085}, {"id": 275247, "content": "必须吃特产", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266847}, {"id": 275248, "content": "这个看上去不错，试一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069398}, {"id": 275249, "content": "网上的旅游攻略说某个很火的地方其实不如附近的另一个地方…然后去了另一个地方，不错哈！当最后要走的时候路过很火的地方看上去还是这里好啊！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308875}, {"id": 275250, "content": "坑太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311680}, {"id": 275506, "content": "年轻就要多走走多看看祖国的大好河山！回到家就会发现还是躺床上玩手机舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124233}, {"id": 275252, "content": "云南买了一套棉麻质地的中服、买的时候幻想啥时候穿合适、买回来三年从来没穿过一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076357}, {"id": 275253, "content": "x小姐的店", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144289}, {"id": 275256, "content": "各式各样小吃街，西安的，厦门的，成都的，贵阳的，丽江的，大理的，青岛的，上海的，南京的，苏州的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311810}, {"id": 275257, "content": "当做支援贫困山区了...其实...就是坑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667188}, {"id": 276793, "content": "吃：全国连锁店的东西是最酷的选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321043}, {"id": 275258, "content": "都说免税店的东西便宜，但都不是便宜的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310556}, {"id": 275259, "content": "去著名景点大皇宫，堪比春运火车站～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310556}, {"id": 275260, "content": "买都买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311218}, {"id": 275774, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134556}, {"id": 275263, "content": "小卖部卖的东西比平常贵几倍 但你有很需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215439}, {"id": 275775, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134556}, {"id": 275265, "content": "楼外楼、松鹤楼这种一看就是坑但是不吃总觉得不对的地方？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311158}]}